readable.content: A dog jumps over a very high barrier at a competition A woman leads a dog to jump a tall hurdle in a competition . Lady in blue top and dark pants astride a white and brown dog leaping a hurdle . The dog jumps over the high jump bars in a dog show as the owner looks on . The woman is guiding a brown and white dog over a tall white fence on an obstacle course .
